Financial tables

Tables in the Egyptian Gazette were produced using boilerplates. This page’s database contains a complete set of these tables. Use the images and links to text below, or consult the separate database, XML files, or image files. - Table boilerplates - copy and paste for standard-format tables, then fill in the details that change from issue to issue.
